title: Food Pack 01
description: A collection of Fruits, Vegetable, Bread Assets created using photogrammetry. 111 Models
longDescription:
High quality collection of fruits, vegetables, breads created using photogrammetry.

62 unique food items with various sliced and cut in half versions, 111 models all together

All With 2k PBR textures

The material for the donuts have the sprinkles and frosting masked out to change the tint colors.

technicalDetails:
Physically-Based Rendering: Yes
Texture Size: 152 - 2048x2048, 3 - 2048x4096, 15 - 2048x1024
Collision: Yes, automatically generated
Vertex Count: 50-1200 tris
LODs: Yes, LOD1 and LOD2
Number of Meshes: 111
Number of Materials and Material Instances: 2 Masters, 58 Instances
Number of Textures: 174 (Diffuse, Compact RGB for Roughness/AO, Normal)
Intended Platform: Desktop
Platforms Tested: Desktop (Windows)
Documentation Included: No
